TTime - A Techinon Timetable utility
------------------------------------

This is the Ruby version of TTime. To run it, you'll need the following
packages (for ruby1.8):

* rake
* ruby1.8
* libzip-ruby1.8
* libgettext-ruby1.8
* libglade2-ruby1.8
* libgtk2-ruby1.8
* libpango1-ruby1.8
* librsvg2-ruby1.8
* libcairo-ruby1.8
* libxml-ruby1.8


UDonkey's XML format (http://udonkey.org)
--------------------

We intend to be compatible with the UDonkey's XML format.  At this point, you
can place MainDB.xml, as generated by UDonkey, in the data subdirectory, and
the data therein will be loaded directly by TTime.
